::FZ::

FZ frowns, looking at Squizzy. "She told me you wanted to steal credit 
for her experiments and so she tried to terminate her."

He looks at the remains of the two bots, the Iron Fist's computer and 
Zardus' own memory working in his head, "She doesn't sound like she's 
telling the truth though. What did you two work on in the lab?"
